<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.1429em; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">第十三届全国大学生电子商务“创新、创意及创业”挑战赛校级决赛由我院党总支书记蔡平、张沁雨老师、余巍老师作为评委。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 2.1429em; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEKn6UX14wazs5J8XEBDJKKicq5SnXfBMbUHg7e81cS68IfcnibL3skLTfR3Tvy5SHXuVhbE236ibQ14g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="264" height="149" style="width: 264px; height: 149px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.1429em; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大赛分为常规赛和实战赛两部分，参赛团队们借助八分钟PPT展示、10分钟评委提问等方式分别从项目主旨、产品介绍、市场分析、竞争分析、经营及实施策略、管理背景和团队能力等方面对创业方案进行了全面的汇报，PPT<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 31.9998px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;">结束后评委针对各参赛团队的商业问题提出了许多可行性建议。答辩环节气氛热烈，充分展现了新时代大学生独有的青春魅力与创新智慧，也深刻体现了校园良好的师生关系和浓厚的学习氛围。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.1429em; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 30.0006px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p><br/></p>